<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.6.7">
<l>puviyuḷnāṉ kaṇṭatō raṟputaṅ kēḷīr</l>
<l rend="indent">pūṇimēyk kumiḷaṅ kōvalar kūṭṭat</l>
<l>tavaiyuḷnā kattaṇai yāṉkuḻa lūta</l>
<l rend="indent">vamaralō kattaḷa vuñceṉṟi caippa</l>
<l>vaviyuṇā maṟantu vāṉava rellā</l>
<l rend="indent">māyarpā ṭiniṟai yappukun tīṇṭi</l>
<l>ceviyuṇā viṉcuvai koṇṭuma kiḻntu</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvinta ṉaittoṭarn teṉṟumvi ṭārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Listen to the miracle I saw upon the earth!</l>
<l>When he on the serpent bed played [his] flute</l>
<l rend="indent">among the assembly of the young herder clan</l>
<l rend="indent">that was grazing cattle</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the sound arose to the celestial world</l>
<l>[such that] all the celestials, forgetting [their] food offerings,</l>
<l rend="indent">hastened to crowd into the herder village,</l>
<l rend="indent">taking in and delighting in the sweet taste [of his song]</l>
<l rend="indent">with the tongue in [their] ears,</l>
<l>following Govinda everywhere,</l>
<l>they were unable to depart [from him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
